---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Privacy Policy - GÃ¶khan Turhan" description="Privacy policy explaining our data collection practices, analytics usage, and subscription data handling.">
  <main class="container">
    <div class="privacy-page">
      <header class="privacy-header">
        <h1>Privacy Policy</h1>
        <p class="last-updated">Last updated: January 2025</p>
      </header>
      
      <div class="privacy-content">
        <section class="privacy-section">
          <h2>Data Collection Overview</h2>
          <p>
            This website is committed to protecting your privacy. We collect minimal data and are transparent about our practices. Here's what you need to know:
          </p>
        </section>

        <section class="privacy-section">
          <h2>What We Don't Collect</h2>
          <ul>
            <li>Personal information without your explicit consent</li>
            <li>Sensitive personal data</li>
            <li>Data from third-party trackers or advertising networks</li>
            <li>Detailed browsing behavior or profiles</li>
            <li>Location data beyond general geographic regions</li>
          </ul>
        </section>

        <section class="privacy-section">
          <h2>Analytics Data</h2>
          <p>
            We use basic analytics to understand how visitors interact with our site. This includes:
          </p>
          <ul>
            <li><strong>Page views:</strong> Which pages are visited</li>
            <li><strong>Referrer information:</strong> Where visitors come from</li>
            <li><strong>Device information:</strong> General device type and browser</li>
            <li><strong>Geographic data:</strong> Country/region level only</li>
          </ul>
          <p>
            This data is anonymized and used solely to improve the website experience. We do not track individual users or create detailed profiles.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section class="privacy-section">
          <h2>Newsletter Subscriptions</h2>
          <p>
            When you subscribe to our newsletter, your data is collected and managed by <strong>Kit (ConvertKit)</strong>, our email service provider. Here's how it works:
          </p>
          <ul>
            <li><strong>Data collected:</strong> Email address and optional preference selections</li>
            <li><strong>Data processor:</strong> Kit (ConvertKit) handles all subscription data</li>
            <li><strong>Your control:</strong> You can unsubscribe at any time via email links</li>
            <li><strong>Kit's privacy:</strong> Subject to <a href="https://convertkit.com/privacy" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Kit's Privacy Policy</a></li>
          </ul>
          <p>
            We do not store your email address on our servers. All subscription management is handled securely by Kit.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section class="privacy-section">
          <h2>Cookies and Local Storage</h2>
          <p>
            We use minimal cookies and local storage for:
          </p>
          <ul>
            <li><strong>Essential functionality:</strong> Site preferences like dark/light mode</li>
            <li><strong>Privacy notice:</strong> Remembering if you've seen our privacy notice</li>
            <li><strong>Analytics:</strong> Basic usage analytics (anonymized)</li>
          </ul>
          <p>
            No advertising or tracking cookies are used. You can disable cookies in your browser settings, though some site features may be affected.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section class="privacy-section">
          <h2>Third-Party Services</h2>
          <p>
            Our website integrates with these trusted services:
          </p>
          <ul>
            <li><strong>Kit (ConvertKit):</strong> Newsletter subscription management</li>
            <li><strong>GitHub:</strong> Website hosting and version control</li>
            <li><strong>Analytics service:</strong> Basic usage statistics (anonymized)</li>
          </ul>
          <p>
            Each service has its own privacy policy governing data handling.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section class="privacy-section">
          <h2>Data Security</h2>
          <p>
            We implement appropriate security measures:
          </p>
          <ul>
            <li>HTTPS encryption for all data transmission</li>
            <li>No storage of personal data on our servers</li>
            <li>Regular security updates and monitoring</li>
            <li>Minimal data collection principle</li>
          </ul>
        </section>

        <section class="privacy-section">
          <h2>Your Rights</h2>
          <p>
            You have the right to:
          </p>
          <ul>
            <li><strong>Access:</strong> Request information about data we process</li>
            <li><strong>Correction:</strong> Update inaccurate information</li>
            <li><strong>Deletion:</strong> Request removal of your data</li>
            <li><strong>Unsubscribe:</strong> Stop receiving newsletters at any time</li>
            <li><strong>Questions:</strong> Contact us about privacy practices</li>
          </ul>
        </section>

        <section class="privacy-section">
          <h2>Children's Privacy</h2>
          <p>
            This website is not directed at children under 13. We do not knowingly collect personal information from children under 13.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section class="privacy-section">
          <h2>Changes to This Policy</h2>
          <p>
            We may update this privacy policy occasionally. Changes will be posted on this page with an updated date. Significant changes will be communicated via our newsletter.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section class="privacy-section">
          <h2>Contact</h2>
          <p>
            Questions about this privacy policy? Reach out through our <a href="/links">contact page</a> or email directly.
          </p>
        </section>
      </div>
    </div>
  </main>
</Layout>

<style>
  .privacy-page {
    max-width: 800px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }
  
  .privacy-header {
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: 3rem;
    padding-bottom: 2rem;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border-light);
  }
  
  .privacy-header h1 {
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }
  
  .last-updated {
    color: var(--text-muted);
    font-style: italic;
    font-size: 0.9rem;
  }
  
  .privacy-content {
    line-height: 1.7;
  }
  
  .privacy-section {
    margin-bottom: 3rem;
  }
  
  .privacy-section h2 {
    color: var(--text-primary);
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    font-size: 1.5rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    border-bottom: 2px solid var(--border-light);
    padding-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }
  
  .privacy-section p {
    color: var(--text-primary);
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }
  
  .privacy-section ul {
    margin: 1rem 0 1.5rem 1.5rem;
    color: var(--text-primary);
  }
  
  .privacy-section li {
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
    line-height: 1.6;
  }
  
  .privacy-section strong {
    color: var(--text-primary);
    font-weight: 600;
  }
  
  .privacy-section a {
    color: var(--color-primary);
    font-weight: 500;
  }
  
  .privacy-section a:hover {
    color: var(--color-primary-hover);
  }
  
  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .privacy-page {
      padding: 0 1rem;
    }
    
    .privacy-section {
      margin-bottom: 2rem;
    }
    
    .privacy-section h2 {
      font-size: 1.25rem;
    }
  }
</style>